{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Different trucks!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As Trucker Joe, you build up your own freight company. You start with an old, weak truck, but later on, with your hard-earned money, you can buy some seriously cool rigs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818630/extras/UnloadingWoodNew.gif?t=1737658054\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Different companies require specialized trailers!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every type of cargo needs the right trailer! Whether it's delivering heavy construction equipment or frozen pizza, you\u2019ll need the right trailer for the job.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818630/extras/MANFrigoNew.gif?t=1737658054\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You place the companies on the map!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You should strategically consider where to place each company to avoid unnecessary detours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818630/extras/BuildingMapNew.gif?t=1737658054\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2818630?t=1737658054","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818630/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1737658054","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818630/516e606ed49c6053a1b781f53f9f1664f0a5ae6c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737658054","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818630/516e606ed49c6053a1b781f53f9f1664f0a5ae6c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737658054","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Different trucks!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As Tru